WEBVTT

01:52.490 --> 01:57.590
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.660 --> 02:01.950
[Episode 33]

02:25.220 --> 02:26.470
Where is he?

02:27.120 --> 02:28.000
Young lady.

02:29.510 --> 02:30.770
Why are you tailing me?

02:31.630 --> 02:32.430
I...

02:34.480 --> 02:35.680
Who are you, exactly?

02:35.920 --> 02:38.160
You're from the Zheng family, aren't you?

02:38.160 --> 02:39.790
Since you're just one fine young lady,

02:39.790 --> 02:41.510
I'll let you get away with this.

02:41.510 --> 02:42.720
Go and tell Zheng Tao

02:43.040 --> 02:44.720
that I won't easily die.

02:45.000 --> 02:47.460
Warn him to be careful
when walking at night.

02:48.200 --> 02:49.200
Wait, please tell me

02:49.200 --> 02:50.600
who you really are.

02:51.040 --> 02:52.350
Stop following me,

02:52.350 --> 02:53.950
or I won't be this nice to you.

02:54.200 --> 02:55.130
You just said...

02:57.760 --> 02:58.040
Gao Ran!

02:58.040 --> 02:59.570
Don't you dare hurt Fan Yun!

02:59.910 --> 03:01.350
-Your name really is "Gao Ran."
-Tian Xing.

03:01.350 --> 03:02.350
You imposter are

03:02.350 --> 03:03.880
actually targeting me now.

03:04.040 --> 03:05.480
Who on earth are you?

03:06.950 --> 03:09.010
You're all eager to know my name, huh?

03:09.320 --> 03:10.540
What is it that you're trying to do?

03:10.540 --> 03:12.200
I should be the one asking you that.

03:12.200 --> 03:13.790
With no regard to the law,
the Zheng family

03:13.790 --> 03:15.440
detained a gate commander
of the Nine Cities illegally

03:15.440 --> 03:17.040
and attempted to snatch my official seal.

03:17.040 --> 03:19.440
-Your official seal?
-Your official seal.

03:19.630 --> 03:20.350
Hold on.

03:22.200 --> 03:23.390
Are you Liu Mu?

03:26.200 --> 03:27.070
Who are you?

03:28.040 --> 03:29.900
-We're on your side!
-Yes, we are!

03:33.670 --> 03:37.270
So you two are the new gate commanders
appointed by the governor?

03:37.550 --> 03:38.630
Tian Xing and I were both

03:38.630 --> 03:41.230
personally assigned by the governor
to be the gate commanders of Jing City.

03:41.230 --> 03:42.630
Let me comb through this.

03:42.760 --> 03:44.440
The governor thought I was dead,

03:44.440 --> 03:46.640
so he sent two new gate commanders over.

03:47.040 --> 03:48.630
However,
with your official seals being stolen,

03:48.630 --> 03:50.490
you can't prove your identities.

03:51.630 --> 03:54.110
And you're
their dedicated military attaché.

03:54.110 --> 03:54.840
That's good.

03:54.920 --> 03:55.600
This way, I don't need to worry

03:55.600 --> 03:57.350
about being held to blame
by the governor in Ling'an.

03:57.350 --> 03:59.560
I meant to put this emergency in writing
and send a letter

03:59.560 --> 04:01.670
to the governor
at the Qi Residence in Ling'an.

04:01.670 --> 04:04.440
It seems that in your heart,
Gate Cdr. Liu,

04:05.110 --> 04:06.710
I hold quite a special place.

04:06.900 --> 04:07.540
"I"?

04:17.260 --> 04:18.870
It turns out that you and Gao Ran

04:18.870 --> 04:20.600
can swap identities with this.

04:22.720 --> 04:24.320
So you're the governor then?

04:25.190 --> 04:26.190
Yes, exactly.

04:26.600 --> 04:27.720
Who else could I be?

04:28.430 --> 04:29.960
Then the Q-Qi Residence...

04:31.230 --> 04:31.990
Doesn't it mean

04:31.990 --> 04:34.850
that the governor and I
have bonded through a fight?

04:39.310 --> 04:40.190
Gate Cdr. Liu,

04:41.080 --> 04:42.750
there's something I need to tell you.

04:42.750 --> 04:44.430
The fact
that I've swapped identities with Gao Ran

04:44.430 --> 04:45.960
must be kept confidential.

04:46.110 --> 04:47.110
Can you do that?

04:47.960 --> 04:48.430
Yes.

04:50.400 --> 04:51.080
Besides,

04:51.670 --> 04:53.130
for this trip to Jing City,

04:53.310 --> 04:54.400
I hope you can serve as

04:54.400 --> 04:55.720
an Assistant Officer to them

04:55.720 --> 04:57.600
and be with them the entire time.

04:57.600 --> 04:58.530
Will you do that?

05:01.750 --> 05:03.280
I don't care about the title.

05:03.280 --> 05:05.040
Fame and fortune mean nothing to me.

05:05.040 --> 05:06.440
I'd love to follow along.

05:07.550 --> 05:08.080
Good.

05:10.720 --> 05:12.650
Today, by hosting this gathering,

05:12.750 --> 05:15.880
I'd like to invite you merchants
to join Juyun Pavilion.

05:16.350 --> 05:17.240
In the future,

05:17.670 --> 05:20.530
Juyun Pavilion will set up operations
in Jing City.

05:21.210 --> 05:22.890
What if we decline?

05:25.520 --> 05:28.310
Then you will make
an enemy of Juyun Pavilion.

05:29.840 --> 05:30.670
Well...

05:31.370 --> 05:33.570
Young Master Lou, you must be extending

05:33.840 --> 05:36.440
this cordial invitation
for a purpose, right?

05:39.480 --> 05:40.310
Yes.

05:41.480 --> 05:43.920
Right now, I need the help
of everyone present

05:43.920 --> 05:45.230
to draw a map for me.

05:46.550 --> 05:48.750
Please be more explicit, Young Master Lou.

05:48.750 --> 05:50.750
What kind of map do you mean?

05:51.310 --> 05:53.110
The defense layout of Jing City.

05:54.480 --> 05:55.790
I'm afraid we can't

05:55.790 --> 05:57.430
help you with that.

05:57.430 --> 05:59.960
If the Zheng family finds out about it,

05:59.960 --> 06:01.560
we'll be in serious trouble.

06:02.160 --> 06:03.280
It is known to all

06:03.920 --> 06:06.350
that the position
of the Zheng family's clan leader

06:06.350 --> 06:09.920
will definitely be passed
onto Eldest Young Master Zheng.

06:23.430 --> 06:25.640
-It's him.
-How could it be him?

06:40.230 --> 06:44.090
You're saying Eldest Young Master Zheng
will be the next clan leader.

06:44.550 --> 06:46.840
What do you all take me for then?

06:48.350 --> 06:50.350
He seems to be Young Master Shi
of the Zheng family.

06:50.350 --> 06:51.600
-What?
-Really?

06:51.600 --> 06:52.990
Really. I've seen that man.

06:52.990 --> 06:53.840
It truly is him.

06:53.840 --> 06:55.110
He's Young Master Shi.

06:55.110 --> 06:56.430
So this is Young Master Shi.

06:56.430 --> 07:00.360
I am the legitimate grandson
of the previous clan leader, Elder Zheng,

07:02.320 --> 07:05.990
as well as head of Juyun Pavilion
that dominates all the Nine Cities.

07:05.990 --> 07:06.590
Everyone,

07:07.040 --> 07:08.900
you're all veteran businessmen.

07:09.720 --> 07:11.350
With a little consideration,

07:11.350 --> 07:14.430
you'll clearly see
the benefits of joining Juyun Pavilion.

07:14.430 --> 07:16.090
Anyway, I know just one thing.

07:16.550 --> 07:18.210
That is, one is much better off

07:18.840 --> 07:21.370
being friends
with Second Young Master Zheng

07:21.720 --> 07:23.310
than being his foes.

07:24.840 --> 07:25.750
Well...

07:25.750 --> 07:26.790
This matter...

07:27.520 --> 07:28.790
Today, I've already

07:28.790 --> 07:30.080
told you my plan.

07:31.400 --> 07:32.930
Whoever attempts to defy me

07:34.600 --> 07:36.580
will not be able to leave this room.

07:43.240 --> 07:46.680
We all pledge to follow you,
Young Master Shi.

08:04.640 --> 08:05.870
A few months ago,

08:05.870 --> 08:09.130
a fire suddenly happened
in the Gate Commander Residence.

08:10.510 --> 08:12.190
Who had such nerve to set a fire

08:12.280 --> 08:13.720
in the Gate Commander Residence?

08:13.720 --> 08:14.960
When I find the arsonist,

08:14.960 --> 08:16.090
I'll definitely...

08:42.280 --> 08:43.590
This place is so creepy.

08:43.590 --> 08:44.550
Let's work faster.

08:44.550 --> 08:45.360
True that.

08:45.360 --> 08:47.520
The Zheng family already rules Jing City.

08:47.520 --> 08:49.380
Why must they have this official seal?

08:49.380 --> 08:51.100
How foolish of you to say that.

08:51.190 --> 08:52.000
Our job is to do

08:52.000 --> 08:53.330
the masters' bidding.

08:53.360 --> 08:54.760
Don't think or ask about it again.

08:54.760 --> 08:55.670
Be quick.

09:04.230 --> 09:05.120
It's going to rain!

09:05.120 --> 09:05.470
Let's go.

09:05.470 --> 09:06.800
Just leave it like this.

09:07.690 --> 09:10.310
Good thing that I know
the breath-holding technique.

09:10.310 --> 09:11.550
That's how I deceived those two idiots.

09:11.550 --> 09:14.150
Otherwise, I would have died
with grievances.

09:14.790 --> 09:16.310
So, since you came back to life,

09:16.310 --> 09:17.760
you've been lying in wait here, collecting

09:17.760 --> 09:19.190
information about the Nine Cities, right?

09:19.190 --> 09:20.590
I thought about leaving,

09:20.790 --> 09:22.240
but I had no one to turn to.

09:22.240 --> 09:23.310
I thought about going home,

09:23.310 --> 09:24.430
but I had nowhere to call home.

09:24.430 --> 09:26.240
Hearing that Zheng Tao led troops
to Ling'an,

09:26.240 --> 09:27.190
I dared not go anywhere

09:27.190 --> 09:28.790
and chose to stay on standby.

09:28.880 --> 09:29.780
Now, all is fine.

09:29.780 --> 09:30.880
Seeing you guys feels

09:30.880 --> 09:33.010
even better than seeing my own mother.

09:36.000 --> 09:37.000
Why not buy a fish?

09:38.290 --> 09:39.430
This one seems fresh.

09:39.430 --> 09:40.270
I'll take it.

09:40.310 --> 09:40.920
No problem.

09:40.920 --> 09:42.120
Along with these two.

09:42.670 --> 09:43.190
Sir,

09:43.430 --> 09:44.710
you do have a good eye.

09:44.710 --> 09:45.190
Look,

09:45.190 --> 09:46.790
I just caught these fresh fish

09:46.790 --> 09:48.790
from the lake this morning.

09:48.790 --> 09:51.380
Do you never ask the price
before buying anything?

09:51.380 --> 09:52.520
Will it be free of charge if I ask?

09:52.520 --> 09:53.480
Of course it won't.

09:53.480 --> 09:54.680
Then why even bother?

09:56.160 --> 09:57.490
You'll pay for the fish.

09:57.590 --> 09:59.120
Why me?

10:01.400 --> 10:02.880
Sir, here are your fish.

10:02.880 --> 10:03.920
Can you lower the price?

10:03.920 --> 10:05.240
No, I can't.

10:10.640 --> 10:11.510
Take care, sir.

10:28.160 --> 10:29.480
Is everyone here yet?

10:29.950 --> 10:31.760
Eldest Young Master, I wonder

10:31.760 --> 10:34.310
why we were summoned here today.

10:35.550 --> 10:37.760
Has the clan leader ring been recovered

10:38.070 --> 10:40.600
and a new master decided
for the Zheng family?

10:41.880 --> 10:43.210
Don't worry about that.

10:43.790 --> 10:45.190
It is only a matter of time

10:45.590 --> 10:47.430
before I find the clan leader ring.

10:47.430 --> 10:48.830
Without the ring,

10:48.830 --> 10:50.760
many things cannot be done.

10:50.760 --> 10:52.040
-Yes.
-Exactly.

10:52.040 --> 10:52.760
-Indeed.
-Right.

10:52.760 --> 10:53.950
How do we cope without the ring?

10:53.950 --> 10:56.040
What's there to do without the ring?

10:58.190 --> 11:01.240
Desperate times
call for desperate measures.

11:01.950 --> 11:04.480
A lot has happened
in the Zheng family lately.

11:04.590 --> 11:06.070
The old clan leader
passed away unexpectedly.

11:06.070 --> 11:09.070
Zheng Tao's grandfather is being trapped
in Ling'an.

11:09.880 --> 11:12.360
Now, the Zheng family is without a leader.

11:12.360 --> 11:15.490
To add to that, the governor
is breathing down our necks.

11:15.950 --> 11:16.760
I...

11:22.040 --> 11:25.880
hereby recommend myself to temporarily
serve as the Zheng family's clan leader.

11:25.880 --> 11:26.920
A hasty decision, isn't it?

11:26.920 --> 11:27.950
Too much of a rush, right?

11:27.950 --> 11:29.280
So hasty.

11:29.280 --> 11:30.120
-Yes.
-Right.

11:30.120 --> 11:31.000
In the long run...

11:31.000 --> 11:31.550
A bit too hasty, huh?

11:31.550 --> 11:32.760
-Yes.
-Too hasty.

11:34.920 --> 11:36.280
Who agrees to it,

11:38.520 --> 11:39.470
and who objects?

11:42.880 --> 11:45.810
Eldest Young Master,
Young Master Shi just arrived.

12:05.000 --> 12:06.200
What brings you here?

12:06.950 --> 12:09.060
All the key relatives of the Zheng family
are gathered here.

12:09.060 --> 12:10.320
How can I not be around?

12:13.040 --> 12:14.920
Might as well tell you what happened.

12:14.920 --> 12:15.640
Today,

12:16.040 --> 12:20.100
the key relatives here have elected me
as the Zheng family's clan leader.

12:20.160 --> 12:21.920
From today on, I am in charge

12:22.830 --> 12:24.000
of the Zheng family.

12:24.470 --> 12:25.190
Is that so?

12:26.280 --> 12:27.550
Who agreed to it?

12:27.830 --> 12:29.550
Step forward and let me see.

12:36.950 --> 12:37.790
Father.

12:38.330 --> 12:40.050
I want one more piece of candy.

12:42.470 --> 12:43.270
There's none.

12:44.160 --> 12:44.920
Next time,

12:45.250 --> 12:47.000
I'll bring you some more, alright?

12:47.000 --> 12:47.460
What...

12:47.830 --> 12:49.160
What did you feed my son?

12:49.160 --> 12:49.760
Father,

12:49.760 --> 12:52.070
the candy he gave me is so delicious.

12:52.070 --> 12:54.070
Please ask him to give me some more.

12:54.070 --> 12:55.920
I believe you've heard
how the Shadow Slay League

12:55.920 --> 12:56.920
executes tasks.

12:57.920 --> 13:00.500
If Young Master Shi gets to be
the clan leader as he wishes,

13:00.500 --> 13:02.760
everyone will have their share of candy.

13:05.280 --> 13:06.190
Otherwise...

13:08.760 --> 13:09.960
I shall take my leave.

13:24.000 --> 13:26.060
I suppose you're not so popular, Jin.

13:26.160 --> 13:28.430
The clan leader election is approaching.

13:28.430 --> 13:30.240
Why rush to become an acting master

13:30.240 --> 13:31.670
at this time?

13:31.670 --> 13:32.710
Zheng Shi.

13:35.160 --> 13:37.160
No need for such sarcastic remarks.

13:39.430 --> 13:40.280
Everyone,

13:40.920 --> 13:43.070
with my grandfather gone
and the gate commander missing,

13:43.070 --> 13:44.640
Jing City is in chaos.

13:44.690 --> 13:47.040
Worried about the instability
in Jing City, the governor

13:47.040 --> 13:49.670
appointed Fan Yun and Tian Xing
to be the new gate commanders here.

13:49.670 --> 13:50.600
It is also a test.

13:51.160 --> 13:52.190
As expected,

13:53.070 --> 13:55.530
the Zheng family is divided
and lacks unity.

13:56.950 --> 13:59.070
I wish to take my grandfather's place
in guarding Jing City.

13:59.070 --> 14:01.550
For that, I have to resort to
extreme measures.

14:01.550 --> 14:02.610
Please forgive me.

14:04.280 --> 14:05.740
Who do you think you are...

14:09.610 --> 14:12.270
to even talk about
protecting the Zheng family?

14:14.590 --> 14:18.050
Fan Yun is absolutely involved
in the old clan leader's death.

14:18.360 --> 14:19.920
You are so close to her.

14:20.190 --> 14:21.070
Zheng Shi,

14:21.640 --> 14:24.570
you plan to be a lackey
for the Nine Cities, don't you?

14:27.190 --> 14:29.470
It is an unfounded speculation
that Fan Yun is related

14:29.470 --> 14:31.130
to my grandfather's passing.

14:31.520 --> 14:32.830
Now that you are all so wary of Fan Yun,

14:32.830 --> 14:34.290
who will take office soon,

14:34.790 --> 14:37.050
I volunteer to solve the problem myself.

14:42.090 --> 14:43.360
I am going to marry her.

14:46.280 --> 14:47.680
You're marrying Fan Yun?

14:48.670 --> 14:49.520
That's right.

14:50.040 --> 14:51.120
After I marry Fan Yun,

14:51.120 --> 14:53.050
she'll be part of the Zheng family.

14:53.400 --> 14:54.920
We the Zheng family members

14:54.920 --> 14:56.780
never give each other a hard time.

14:57.210 --> 14:58.960
What do you think of this solution?

14:58.960 --> 15:00.390
It's worth a try.

15:00.670 --> 15:02.520
Sounds like a safe option.

15:04.400 --> 15:05.160
Brilliant.

15:05.920 --> 15:06.980
This is brilliant.

15:07.710 --> 15:09.280
During the clan leader election,

15:09.280 --> 15:11.430
no one but Zheng family members
can enter Jing City.

15:11.430 --> 15:13.890
If Fan Yun becomes
my second sister-in-law,

15:14.160 --> 15:15.430
she'll be allowed into the city
to take office, right?

15:15.430 --> 15:16.960
That's not going to happen!

15:17.590 --> 15:18.400
Zheng Shi,

15:19.670 --> 15:22.190
you're actually trying to help Fan Yun
take up her post

15:22.190 --> 15:24.320
by proposing to marry her, aren't you?

15:25.360 --> 15:29.310
It is the governor's decision to make
Fan Yun a gate commander of Jing City.

15:29.310 --> 15:30.920
How is my help even needed?

15:32.000 --> 15:34.530
I guess someone just wants
to stand in her way.

15:36.900 --> 15:38.310
The position of gate commander

15:38.310 --> 15:39.520
for Jing City will still be taken

15:39.520 --> 15:41.190
by someone else, if not Fan Yun.

15:41.190 --> 15:42.400
Suppose she doesn't take office

15:42.400 --> 15:44.280
and a new gate commander is assigned
by the Nine Cities,

15:44.280 --> 15:45.610
what are you going to do?

15:45.670 --> 15:48.640
Irritating the Nine Cities by keeping
a new gate commander from her post...

15:48.640 --> 15:49.430
Jin,

15:50.470 --> 15:52.310
are you attempting a rebellion?

15:54.100 --> 15:55.700
Have you thought it through?

16:00.670 --> 16:02.670
Sir, don't let him get your goat.

16:03.400 --> 16:04.930
And don't forget your plan.

16:09.000 --> 16:09.760
Fine.

16:11.120 --> 16:13.050
Since you have the gut to marry her,

16:16.310 --> 16:18.040
I'll arrange a wedding for you.

16:24.430 --> 16:26.090
I'll leave it to you then, Jin.

16:27.790 --> 16:29.990
The few of us can't eat this much, right?

16:30.790 --> 16:32.920
Your Excellency, it's a good thing
you were born into the Qi family.

16:32.920 --> 16:33.430
If you were born

16:33.430 --> 16:34.880
-into an ordinary family...
-I bought this much

16:34.880 --> 16:36.810
because you were paying, alright?

16:38.360 --> 16:39.490
Fan Yun told me

16:40.120 --> 16:41.650
that one must eat properly,

16:41.710 --> 16:43.240
regardless of any happenings.

16:43.240 --> 16:45.040
The stomach is not to be mistreated.

16:45.040 --> 16:46.180
That is true.

16:46.640 --> 16:49.640
One can't come up with any ideas
with an empty stomach.

16:53.310 --> 16:54.160
Listen,

16:54.760 --> 16:56.470
how about you disguise yourself a bit?

16:56.470 --> 16:58.120
If the Zheng family finds out
you're still alive,

16:58.120 --> 16:59.720
there will be trouble again.

17:00.190 --> 17:02.550
Your Excellency,
why not disguise yourself too?

17:02.550 --> 17:03.520
If the Zheng family finds out

17:03.520 --> 17:04.880
the governor is walking around the street,

17:04.880 --> 17:07.410
it'll be more likely to cause trouble,
right?

17:07.940 --> 17:10.710
You didn't know I'm the governor at first,
did you?

17:10.710 --> 17:11.640
Outside Ling'an City,

17:11.640 --> 17:13.750
who knows what the governor looks like?

17:13.750 --> 17:14.920
If you ask me,

17:15.349 --> 17:17.319
these whiskers of yours are really...

17:17.319 --> 17:18.190
a giveaway.

17:19.319 --> 17:21.250
Your Excellency, you have no idea.

17:21.319 --> 17:23.030
Without these whiskers,

17:23.030 --> 17:24.760
I'd look absolutely handsome.

17:26.359 --> 17:27.510
No bragging.

17:27.670 --> 17:28.230
I...

17:48.050 --> 17:49.650
That's from Juyun Pavilion.

17:59.080 --> 18:00.520
How magnificent.

18:00.550 --> 18:02.350
Must be an influential family.

18:02.840 --> 18:04.640
Gentlemen... what's this for?

18:05.160 --> 18:06.840
We're delivering betrothal gifts
from the Zheng family.

18:06.840 --> 18:07.230
The main item

18:07.230 --> 18:09.430
is a pair of live wild geese
from Jing City,

18:09.430 --> 18:10.840
along with countless secondary gifts.

18:10.840 --> 18:12.640
This is to propose marriage
for the second son of the legitimate line,

18:12.640 --> 18:15.640
Zheng Shi, to the precious daughter
of the Fan family.

18:17.600 --> 18:18.230
For who?

18:19.360 --> 18:20.120
Zheng Shi?

18:20.750 --> 18:22.850
I'm also confused. Are you saying

18:23.190 --> 18:24.650
Second Young Master Zheng

18:24.800 --> 18:26.120
w-wants to marry me?

18:26.880 --> 18:27.950
Exactly, Your Ladyship.

18:27.950 --> 18:28.990
"Your Ladyship"?

18:29.560 --> 18:30.560
This is Lord Fan.

18:31.620 --> 18:32.550
Lord Fan came to Jing City

18:32.550 --> 18:33.800
for important issues.

18:33.800 --> 18:35.400
She's not to be trifled with.

18:36.230 --> 18:37.230
Calm down.

18:37.230 --> 18:38.470
I think there is

18:38.470 --> 18:39.650
probably a reason for it.

18:39.650 --> 18:40.780
Let me ask him again.

18:42.750 --> 18:44.080
What else did

18:44.080 --> 18:45.280
Young Master Shi say?

18:45.320 --> 18:46.670
He also said

18:46.670 --> 18:47.920
that Eldest Young Master has set up

18:47.920 --> 18:49.600
an inescapable trap at the city gate.

18:49.600 --> 18:51.680
Lord Fan, if you enter the city
at this time,

18:51.680 --> 18:53.940
there is no way to guarantee your safety.

18:55.400 --> 18:56.920
To help you gain entry,

18:56.920 --> 18:57.670
Young Master Shi

18:57.670 --> 18:59.640
proposes that you should be carried
in this bridal sedan chair

18:59.640 --> 19:01.250
into the city as his future wife.

19:01.250 --> 19:02.330
When this is done,

19:02.360 --> 19:04.090
he won't force you to marry him.

19:04.280 --> 19:05.930
He won't force me to marry him?

19:05.930 --> 19:07.300
What did I tell you?

19:07.330 --> 19:09.310
That man has long had his eye on you.

19:09.330 --> 19:11.060
Even before you enter the city,

19:11.070 --> 19:12.600
he has already shown a tell.

19:16.840 --> 19:18.230
Go and tell your boss

19:18.800 --> 19:20.800
to spare us all these fancy excuses.

19:21.270 --> 19:23.670
We'll find a way to enter the city
on our own.

19:24.080 --> 19:25.810
Take your things and leave now.

19:25.990 --> 19:26.390
Scram!

19:26.800 --> 19:28.800
Well, please leave.

19:28.800 --> 19:30.260
We'll discuss the matter.

19:30.400 --> 19:31.730
I'll take my leave then.

19:32.350 --> 19:32.880
Let's go.

19:36.920 --> 19:37.710
Discuss?

19:43.750 --> 19:44.560
Easy on the tea.

19:44.560 --> 19:46.290
Don't gulp down the tea leaves.

19:47.230 --> 19:49.030
Or the result won't be accurate.

19:50.120 --> 19:50.850
Here you are.

19:51.190 --> 19:52.320
Perform a divination.

19:52.320 --> 19:54.780
Find out when Fan Yun and others
will be back.

20:01.710 --> 20:03.270
The tea leaves show the people

20:03.270 --> 20:05.990
you're thinking about
have no fixed date of return.

20:05.990 --> 20:07.520
It's a rather ominous sign.

20:08.360 --> 20:09.430
Take a closer look.

20:09.430 --> 20:11.120
The tea leaves fell off the side,
leading to an inaccurate reading.

20:11.120 --> 20:12.840
I did tell you to slow down
on the drinking.

20:12.840 --> 20:13.800
This doesn't count.

20:13.800 --> 20:14.330
Next one.

20:22.600 --> 20:24.200
I don't need any divination.

20:24.800 --> 20:26.260
Are you looking down on me?

20:26.320 --> 20:27.120
Of course not.

20:27.470 --> 20:28.920
Then why won't you let me
perform a divination for you?

20:28.920 --> 20:29.840
-I...
-If Gao Ran were here,

20:29.840 --> 20:31.440
he'd definitely let me do it.

20:31.920 --> 20:32.750
Fine then.

20:33.360 --> 20:35.820
Perform a divination then.
On what, though?

20:40.600 --> 20:42.260
How about your romantic life?

20:42.720 --> 20:43.320
I...

20:45.220 --> 20:46.080
Hurry up.

20:46.230 --> 20:47.030
Drink the tea.

20:53.560 --> 20:55.710
Do it now. Drink it.

21:14.900 --> 21:16.710
The star of romance is in motion.

21:16.800 --> 21:18.200
What an auspicious sign!

21:18.400 --> 21:19.950
But it is pointing to...

21:19.950 --> 21:20.710
Wait.

21:20.710 --> 21:21.750
How come it is not

21:21.750 --> 21:23.950
pointing to Jing City, where Fan Yun is?

21:26.920 --> 21:28.120
You'd better look closely.

21:28.120 --> 21:29.360
Who is it suggesting?

21:42.670 --> 21:43.640
Report!

21:46.550 --> 21:48.270
Zheng Tao from Jing City and Lord Lyu

21:48.270 --> 21:50.070
are brawling at the palace gate!

21:51.320 --> 21:52.720
How can they have a fight?

21:53.160 --> 21:53.640
Come on.

21:53.950 --> 21:55.950
Quickly take me to Huiyun Pavilion.

21:58.380 --> 22:00.220
Oh, Zheng Tao...

22:01.320 --> 22:02.320
Your Excellency,

22:02.360 --> 22:02.950
as I was

22:02.950 --> 22:05.160
coming out of the counsel hall
after finishing

22:05.160 --> 22:06.320
some official business,

22:06.320 --> 22:08.120
I bumped into him at the gate.

22:08.120 --> 22:09.160
Without saying a word,

22:09.160 --> 22:10.620
he came up and attacked me.

22:11.400 --> 22:11.990
Look,

22:11.990 --> 22:13.800
he even torn off my belt.

22:13.800 --> 22:16.300
Give the ring back and I'll call it quits.

22:18.470 --> 22:19.320
Ring?

22:19.880 --> 22:20.670
What ring?

22:25.470 --> 22:27.730
The clan leader ring of the Zhang family?

22:28.400 --> 22:29.400
How could I possibly have

22:29.400 --> 22:30.800
such an important item?

22:33.400 --> 22:34.400
See for yourself!

22:48.030 --> 22:48.800
This...

22:50.640 --> 22:52.080
I can explain it to you.

22:52.560 --> 22:53.470
Last time

22:53.470 --> 22:55.320
when I had a falling-out

22:55.320 --> 22:56.560
with Zheng,

22:56.560 --> 22:58.640
he smashed the stuff that he gave me

22:58.640 --> 22:59.750
as a gift.

22:59.750 --> 23:00.710
He then fixed it

23:00.710 --> 23:02.670
and sent it back to me.

23:04.360 --> 23:06.480
That's why I wrote "received" here.

23:10.710 --> 23:11.640
Oh, Zheng,

23:11.640 --> 23:14.080
I was wondering
why you made me write a receipt.

23:14.080 --> 23:16.410
As it turns out,
this is your real purpose.

23:16.880 --> 23:18.660
Zheng, you really got me

23:18.920 --> 23:20.880
into trouble, didn't you?

23:20.880 --> 23:21.990
I don't care.

23:21.990 --> 23:23.640
It is a fact that when my brother died,

23:23.640 --> 23:24.750
only this man was with him.

23:24.750 --> 23:26.280
You must be the right person

23:26.710 --> 23:28.310
who I should ask for the ring!

23:30.640 --> 23:32.100
THis is utterly improper.

23:34.470 --> 23:35.160
Lord Lyu.

23:35.950 --> 23:36.750
Tell me.

23:37.710 --> 23:38.820
Where is

23:39.120 --> 23:40.520
the clan leader ring now?

23:41.000 --> 23:41.530
Wait, no.

23:41.990 --> 23:42.600
I...

23:45.750 --> 23:47.030
I-I...

23:53.880 --> 23:54.560
How would I know

23:54.560 --> 23:56.420
where that ring of your family is?

23:56.710 --> 23:58.170
Be reasonable, Zheng Tao!

24:46.230 --> 24:47.360
Hungry, aren't you?

24:48.160 --> 24:50.190
Try this. See if you like it.

24:51.270 --> 24:53.230
No. I don't have an appetite for it.

24:55.030 --> 24:56.600
You haven't had a proper meal

24:56.600 --> 24:59.010
along the entire journey.

24:59.360 --> 25:00.690
Please just have a bite.

25:01.840 --> 25:02.510
Fan Yun,

25:03.400 --> 25:04.200
let me ask you.

25:05.190 --> 25:06.790
What exactly is on your mind?

25:08.990 --> 25:11.160
We just had the sweet dew tea that day,
didn't we?

25:11.160 --> 25:11.800
Now, are you

25:11.800 --> 25:13.400
going to marry someone else?

25:14.190 --> 25:15.750
No, of course not.

25:17.990 --> 25:19.560
Didn't those people just say

25:19.560 --> 25:22.400
it was only an expedient plan to carry me
in the bridal sedan chair into the city?

25:22.400 --> 25:23.920
It is in fact just feigning a marriage.

25:23.920 --> 25:25.120
All of it is a mere act.

25:26.430 --> 25:28.090
Besides, isn't gaining entry

25:28.320 --> 25:29.990
to the city our priority now?

25:30.560 --> 25:32.690
-Don't you think so?
-No more talking.

25:34.990 --> 25:36.250
I've figured out a way.

25:39.160 --> 25:40.560
You've figured out a way?

25:41.270 --> 25:42.530
How should we proceed?

25:46.190 --> 25:47.080
What is this?

25:47.670 --> 25:48.870
The clan leader ring.

25:53.080 --> 25:55.140
The Zheng family's clan leader ring.

25:55.430 --> 25:56.640
Why do you have it?

25:57.270 --> 25:58.670
Elder Zheng gave it to me.

26:00.530 --> 26:02.180
By giving me this ring,

26:03.160 --> 26:05.090
he meant to entrust Jing City to me.

26:06.160 --> 26:07.640
The root cause of the Zheng family's mess

26:07.640 --> 26:08.880
lies not in the surface,

26:08.880 --> 26:10.010
but deep in the core.

26:10.360 --> 26:12.360
So, the real purpose
of my trip to Jing City

26:12.360 --> 26:14.360
is to first nip the brewing unrest

26:14.620 --> 26:15.880
in Jing City in the bud,

26:16.360 --> 26:18.430
and to select a proper clan leader
for the Zheng family

26:18.430 --> 26:20.290
to boost Jing City's prosperity.

26:20.670 --> 26:21.640
Only by doing so

26:21.920 --> 26:23.600
will peace be restored for the people
in Jing City

26:23.600 --> 26:25.330
and the rest of the Nine Cities.

26:25.750 --> 26:26.410
Therefore,

26:27.430 --> 26:29.230
now, with this ring, perhaps we can

26:29.230 --> 26:30.960
enter the city without hustle.

26:35.080 --> 26:36.120
I see.

26:37.640 --> 26:40.640
Then, what took you so long
to finally tell me about it?

26:41.600 --> 26:42.990
I was planning to assess the situation

26:42.990 --> 26:43.840
upon arriving in Jing City

26:43.840 --> 26:45.440
before telling you the truth

26:45.640 --> 26:47.170
and discussing it with you.

26:49.510 --> 26:50.570
Oh right, Qi Zheng.

26:51.640 --> 26:52.600
Who else

26:52.990 --> 26:53.990
knows about this?

26:54.470 --> 26:55.640
Only you and me.

26:56.800 --> 26:58.400
Only the two of us?

27:02.190 --> 27:03.510
It doesn't feel right.

27:05.920 --> 27:07.120
The Zheng family

27:07.120 --> 27:08.710
have no scruples now.

27:10.560 --> 27:11.750
When a non-member of the Zheng family

27:11.750 --> 27:13.320
holds out this ring,

27:13.320 --> 27:14.650
will they be convinced?

27:17.560 --> 27:18.960
Even if the answer is yes,

27:19.080 --> 27:20.480
after entering the city,

27:20.600 --> 27:22.800
we'll surely become the target for all.

27:23.560 --> 27:24.420
Think about it.

27:25.320 --> 27:27.850
The fact
that Elder Zheng gave this ring to you

27:28.270 --> 27:29.200
means he already

27:29.270 --> 27:31.600
knew his family members were at variance.

27:32.120 --> 27:33.520
At this particular time,

27:33.710 --> 27:34.670
Zheng Shi willingly

27:34.670 --> 27:35.880
lends us a helping hand

27:35.880 --> 27:37.230
in suppressing the Zheng family.

27:37.230 --> 27:38.800
Why don't we play along?

27:39.230 --> 27:40.230
What's the point

27:40.600 --> 27:41.950
of finding another way?

27:43.080 --> 27:44.360
This is just too risky.

27:47.470 --> 27:48.870
You say no to everything.

27:49.560 --> 27:52.490
Is there any other way
besides letting you marry him?

28:00.750 --> 28:01.470
Oh, wait.

28:02.800 --> 28:04.260
What if I insist on finding

28:04.510 --> 28:06.440
a different way despite all risks?

28:09.560 --> 28:10.240
Come here.

28:15.990 --> 28:17.400
W-What?

28:17.920 --> 28:18.740
Trust me.

28:19.500 --> 28:20.900
It will definitely work.

28:40.260 --> 28:41.130
It's you.

28:42.400 --> 28:44.460
Yes. Didn't see this coming, did you?

28:44.650 --> 28:46.890
But in others' eyes,

28:47.360 --> 28:48.960
the case might be different.

28:49.560 --> 28:50.660
Anyway,

28:51.120 --> 28:52.250
I owe you a thank you.

28:52.800 --> 28:54.220
I'm just doing what I should.

28:54.220 --> 28:56.670
I'm afraid you can't stay
at the Gate Commander Residence anymore.

28:56.670 --> 28:57.490
Nonetheless, I've prepared

28:57.490 --> 28:59.160
a room for you in the Zheng Residence.

28:59.160 --> 28:59.920
Hold on.

29:00.560 --> 29:01.910
This is enough acting.

29:02.080 --> 29:03.430
Don't push your luck

29:03.470 --> 29:05.070
or forget who you really are.

29:06.320 --> 29:08.520
Lord Gao, how come you've been sounding

29:09.800 --> 29:11.200
a bit jealous these days?

29:12.120 --> 29:13.180
Do I sound jealous?

29:14.920 --> 29:16.800
Thank you for such kindness,
Second Young Master Zheng.

29:16.800 --> 29:18.160
We need to get in to deal with

29:18.160 --> 29:19.320
official business.

29:19.880 --> 29:22.140
We'd rather not bother the Zheng family.

29:22.320 --> 29:23.520
I'll walk you in then.

29:25.530 --> 29:27.600
What place you think
the Gate Commander Residence is?

29:27.600 --> 29:29.230
It's a government office of importance.

29:29.230 --> 29:30.580
Plain commoners such as yourself

29:30.580 --> 29:31.870
had better stay out.

29:33.990 --> 29:35.360
Not just Jing City–

29:35.360 --> 29:36.360
in the entire Ling'an,

29:36.360 --> 29:38.020
there isn't a place I can't go.

29:40.480 --> 29:41.950
Second Young Master Zheng,

29:41.950 --> 29:43.630
I think Gao Ran has a point.

29:43.990 --> 29:46.990
The Gate Commander Residence
is indeed a government office.

29:46.990 --> 29:48.400
It wouldn't be appropriate to let you

29:48.400 --> 29:49.730
come and go freely here.

29:49.800 --> 29:51.670
It'll cause much trouble

29:51.670 --> 29:52.880
if people hold it against you.

29:52.880 --> 29:53.430
Fine.

29:54.920 --> 29:55.920
You care about me,

29:56.030 --> 29:57.230
so I'll listen to you.

29:57.340 --> 29:57.890
Let's go.

29:59.270 --> 30:01.400
Thank you, Second Young Master Zheng!

30:03.360 --> 30:05.230
Shi has really gone crazy.

30:05.750 --> 30:08.750
He actually opened the city gate
to welcome Fan Yun in.

30:09.510 --> 30:11.510
What a disgrace to the Zheng family.

30:13.750 --> 30:15.710
Please don't be mad, Eldest Young Master.

30:15.710 --> 30:17.120
Today's bride welcoming ceremony

30:17.120 --> 30:18.600
was simply a bluff.

30:19.270 --> 30:20.430
It was not held

30:20.430 --> 30:21.320
in a legitimate name

30:21.320 --> 30:22.470
or a proper way.

30:23.230 --> 30:24.920
How can I not be mad?

30:25.950 --> 30:27.160
At this rate,

30:27.640 --> 30:29.710
I'm afraid even the Zheng ancestors
in heaven

30:29.710 --> 30:30.950
would be enraged.

30:31.430 --> 30:32.320
In my opinion,

30:32.710 --> 30:34.710
this is not necessarily a bad thing.

30:34.750 --> 30:35.750
You see, sir,

30:36.190 --> 30:38.230
the clan leader ring
is nowhere to be found.

30:38.230 --> 30:39.320
It seems

30:39.320 --> 30:41.470
that the election has lost its basis.

30:41.470 --> 30:42.640
That said, in this situation,

30:42.640 --> 30:44.990
people's support weighs more in choosing

30:44.990 --> 30:46.670
the next clan leader.

30:48.750 --> 30:49.840
People's support?

30:51.190 --> 30:52.840
What Young Master Shi did today has truly

30:52.840 --> 30:54.440
brought shame to the family.

30:55.470 --> 30:56.710
The key relatives of the Zheng family

30:56.710 --> 30:59.440
and even everyone else in Jing City
witnessed it.

30:59.640 --> 31:00.440
After all,

31:00.670 --> 31:03.070
no one hopes
that the master of their choice

31:03.430 --> 31:05.030
is a weak and incompetent man

31:05.320 --> 31:07.520
who disgraces the Zheng family, right?

31:08.000 --> 31:09.570
You do have a point.

31:11.120 --> 31:13.790
Shi degraded himself
in order to marry Fan Yun,

31:13.820 --> 31:16.430
practically to the state
of kneeling and begging.

31:16.430 --> 31:17.960
It was a sheer disgrace.

31:23.750 --> 31:25.150
How are things going?

31:25.600 --> 31:27.430
Has all the stuff arrived
at the warehouse?

31:27.430 --> 31:28.690
Yes, every piece of it.

31:36.230 --> 31:39.090
I see you've been getting quite close
to Shi lately.

31:39.640 --> 31:41.230
Do you intend to follow in his footsteps

31:41.230 --> 31:42.750
and try to humiliate me?

31:44.670 --> 31:45.730
Why would I do that?

31:45.950 --> 31:47.080
I'm just feeling...

31:47.290 --> 31:48.420
I'm just feeling...

31:52.710 --> 31:54.670
there must be misunderstanding
between you two.

31:54.670 --> 31:57.200
I'd hate to see you brothers
fight each other.

32:02.160 --> 32:04.360
What misunderstanding could there be?

32:05.600 --> 32:06.470
Are you trying

32:06.470 --> 32:08.430
to put in a good word for him with me?

32:08.920 --> 32:10.850
You should look at what he has done.

32:13.750 --> 32:14.950
Shi must have done...

32:15.120 --> 32:17.580
what he did
in the Zheng family's interests.

32:18.160 --> 32:20.360
Fan Yun is from the Fan family after all.

32:20.360 --> 32:22.290
She's also the new gate commander.

32:22.600 --> 32:23.360
If...

32:23.750 --> 32:25.710
she marries into the Zheng family,

32:26.080 --> 32:27.230
many problems

32:27.230 --> 32:28.490
will be easily solved.

32:29.120 --> 32:31.920
The whole Zheng family
will be greatly encouraged

32:32.670 --> 32:35.080
and break away from our current decline.

32:46.840 --> 32:49.470
Seems like the Gate Commander Residence
hasn't been

32:49.470 --> 32:51.800
attended to for a long time
since the fire.

32:52.320 --> 32:54.230
After what happened to Gate Cdr. Liu,

32:54.230 --> 32:55.560
with no leaders or any motivation

32:55.560 --> 32:57.360
to govern Jing City, the other officials

32:57.360 --> 32:59.560
have become completely disorganized.

33:04.190 --> 33:05.650
With the core pillar gone,

33:06.120 --> 33:08.720
they've certainly lost the will
to run things.

33:09.880 --> 33:11.470
I bet you can't imagine

33:11.470 --> 33:13.950
how important I am in their hearts.

33:15.560 --> 33:16.470
Gate Commander,

33:16.470 --> 33:18.730
the Zheng family sent us here to help out.

33:20.230 --> 33:22.360
Must be spies sent by the Zheng family.

33:22.920 --> 33:24.180
Let's talk in private.

33:24.880 --> 33:26.500
Thank you then.

33:26.710 --> 33:29.030
We have to handle government business now.

33:29.030 --> 33:29.670
Let's go.

33:32.640 --> 33:34.080
Move, guys.

33:36.670 --> 33:38.270
The Zheng family captured me

33:38.360 --> 33:40.120
and locked me in a dungeon.

33:40.510 --> 33:42.510
It was all because of this.

33:43.120 --> 33:44.250
I nearly lost my life

33:44.710 --> 33:46.870
due to this small piece of stone.

33:47.190 --> 33:48.950
But still, I find

33:49.560 --> 33:51.030
one thing strange.

33:51.430 --> 33:52.510
What is it?

33:53.160 --> 33:54.070
Think about it.

33:54.430 --> 33:56.430
Suppose the Zheng family
just set that fire

33:56.430 --> 33:59.230
at the Gate Commander Residence
to secretly seize power,

33:59.230 --> 34:01.510
they could've taken complete control

34:01.510 --> 34:03.160
of Jing City

34:03.600 --> 34:04.930
after Elder Zheng died.

34:05.470 --> 34:07.360
They didn't even
care for the gate commander.

34:07.360 --> 34:10.219
Why would they try to
get hold of this official seal?

34:11.070 --> 34:12.030
Right.

34:12.360 --> 34:14.239
Is it their plan to take this post?

34:15.150 --> 34:16.989
But even if they had this official seal,

34:16.989 --> 34:18.989
they couldn't be the gate commander.

34:18.989 --> 34:20.510
These days, I've been thinking

34:20.510 --> 34:22.429
about this question as well, but it still

34:22.429 --> 34:24.290
remains a tangled mess in my head.

34:25.400 --> 34:28.060
Maybe they were trying to keep us
out of the city,

34:28.110 --> 34:30.040
yet we would get in sooner or later.

34:30.219 --> 34:32.449
Maybe they meant to eliminate all of us,

34:32.630 --> 34:35.199
yet someone else besides us
would be sent over.

34:35.199 --> 34:37.600
Why exactly did they
go to all that trouble?

34:38.199 --> 34:39.400
Your Excellency,

34:39.400 --> 34:40.630
what are you writing?

34:45.030 --> 34:46.560
Give me your official seal.

34:52.480 --> 34:54.360
"The gate commander hereby orders

34:54.360 --> 34:56.199
that all taxes will be halved."

34:56.510 --> 34:57.680
Why would you write this

34:57.680 --> 34:59.080
at this particular time?

34:59.680 --> 35:00.430
Watch this.

35:03.030 --> 35:03.800
Indeed,

35:04.280 --> 35:06.150
this truly is just a small piece of jade.

35:06.150 --> 35:07.920
It can't be called an official seal.

35:07.920 --> 35:08.990
At most,

35:08.990 --> 35:10.510
holding it can prove one's identity.

35:10.510 --> 35:12.280
Apart from that, nothing can be done.

35:12.280 --> 35:14.010
Only when it's applied on paper

35:14.430 --> 35:16.290
can it be called an official seal.

35:16.430 --> 35:17.360
That is to say,

35:17.760 --> 35:19.420
the Zheng family are actually

35:19.720 --> 35:22.050
after the power behind the official seal.

35:22.510 --> 35:23.070
Correct.

35:23.470 --> 35:24.270
Gate Cdr. Liu,

35:24.800 --> 35:25.760
where are the files kept?

35:25.760 --> 35:28.070
All official files in Jing City
are in duplicate.

35:28.070 --> 35:29.400
One is sent to the Archives,

35:29.400 --> 35:31.280
and the other is kept here.

35:31.280 --> 35:32.200
In recent months,

35:32.200 --> 35:34.330
no one has even come to clean the place.

35:34.590 --> 35:36.550
Although it's a bit messy here,

35:36.550 --> 35:38.110
as long as the files are still around,

35:38.110 --> 35:40.150
we will definitely find some clues.

35:40.150 --> 35:41.510
We have to find out what those

35:41.510 --> 35:44.200
in the Zheng family really want to do
with this official seal.

35:44.200 --> 35:45.280
More importantly,

35:45.630 --> 35:46.490
we must uncover

35:46.590 --> 35:49.050
the mastermind behind all these incidents.

35:49.360 --> 35:51.290
Make sure we catch them red-handed

35:51.470 --> 35:53.630
so as to have them fully submit.

35:55.430 --> 35:56.590
Without further ado,

35:56.590 --> 35:57.720
let's get started.

36:10.720 --> 36:11.470
Wait!

36:20.320 --> 36:20.850
Alright.

36:21.500 --> 36:22.590
There's no pomelo in it.

36:22.590 --> 36:23.590
You may eat it now.

36:30.400 --> 36:31.860
This is utterly improper.

36:51.470 --> 36:52.240
Off you go!

36:56.950 --> 36:58.950
Leave!

37:05.910 --> 37:07.350
Get out of here already!

37:12.300 --> 37:13.930
The more you disturb it,

37:14.030 --> 37:15.280
the louder it gets.

37:46.290 --> 37:47.550
This bird is just lost.

37:54.880 --> 37:55.520
Oh right.

37:56.320 --> 37:58.920
What do you want to see me about?

38:27.590 --> 38:28.590
This isn't right.

38:29.270 --> 38:30.990
This stamp isn't from your seal.

38:30.990 --> 38:33.190
And this is from the one we brought here.

38:33.680 --> 38:34.940
Take a look, everyone.

38:35.110 --> 38:36.800
These two stamps are not the same.

38:36.800 --> 38:37.720
On our way here,

38:37.720 --> 38:38.720
the official seal

38:39.030 --> 38:40.880
was chipped due to the bumpy road.

38:40.880 --> 38:42.480
So the stamp looks like this.

38:42.550 --> 38:44.010
But on the previous files,

38:44.110 --> 38:45.840
the impressions are complete.

38:46.720 --> 38:48.920
Then which documents were stamped
with the new official seal?

38:48.920 --> 38:51.520
All of these are clearance records
at the pier.

38:53.200 --> 38:54.600
The new official seal...

38:55.550 --> 38:56.810
All of this is evidence

38:57.150 --> 38:58.550
that after your "death,"

38:58.550 --> 39:00.880
goods continued to be cleared at the pier.

39:00.880 --> 39:02.950
A batch of supplies were being processed
at Jing City  port previously,

39:02.950 --> 39:03.590
but the weight and price

39:03.590 --> 39:04.880
reported by the staffers

39:04.880 --> 39:06.030
didn't add up.

39:06.030 --> 39:07.070
Such a thing usually happens

39:07.070 --> 39:08.240
when someone tries to smuggle

39:08.240 --> 39:10.110
stuff in, like salt, grain, poison,
iron, and so on.

39:10.110 --> 39:11.510
That's why I put the paper aside
without stamping

39:11.510 --> 39:12.280
the official seal on it.

39:12.280 --> 39:13.240
I planned to check that batch out myself

39:13.240 --> 39:14.240
when I had time.

39:14.240 --> 39:15.920
But I forgot about it as I got busy.

39:15.920 --> 39:17.030
Now, look,

39:17.400 --> 39:19.280
there's already a stamp on it.

39:19.470 --> 39:20.920
It means they took the official seal

39:20.920 --> 39:22.650
specifically for this matter.

39:24.360 --> 39:26.560
But what doesn't the Zheng family have?

39:27.360 --> 39:29.240
Was it really worth so much effort

39:30.210 --> 39:31.730
for some smuggled goods?

39:32.840 --> 39:34.510
What could be so important

39:35.200 --> 39:37.260
that they would risk their lives for?

39:38.760 --> 39:40.320
Enough with the contemplation.

39:40.320 --> 39:42.840
Those things couldn't have flown away,
could they?

39:42.840 --> 39:44.800
We'll find out the truth
if we go take a look, right?

39:44.800 --> 39:46.590
Exactly. The governor is right.

39:46.590 --> 39:48.060
The Jing City dock grants clearance
on dates ending with five.

39:48.060 --> 39:50.030
The supplies are highly likely
to be shipped in tonight.

39:50.030 --> 39:51.240
Today, we should at least find out

39:51.240 --> 39:52.840
where these items are going.

39:53.760 --> 39:55.240
But it's extremely difficult

39:55.240 --> 39:57.370
to gain access to the Zheng Residence.

39:59.590 --> 40:01.990
Everyone, which one of you
is Gate Cdr. Fan?

40:02.920 --> 40:03.630
I am.

40:03.990 --> 40:05.150
The eldest young master
of the Zheng family

40:05.150 --> 40:06.920
is hosting a banquet
at the Zheng Residence tomorrow

40:06.920 --> 40:08.470
to welcome
the new gate commander of Jing City,

40:08.470 --> 40:09.360
who shall assume office soon.

40:09.360 --> 40:11.820
Gate Commander,
please do attend the event.

40:15.720 --> 40:16.430
Here you are.

40:16.430 --> 40:17.760
Now this has saved us much trouble.

40:17.760 --> 40:19.560
They just gave us an invitation.

40:21.800 --> 40:22.470
Alright.

40:23.070 --> 40:24.990
Zheng Jin has invited me over.

40:24.990 --> 40:26.720
Let's split up and take action.

40:27.320 --> 40:29.680
I'd really love to find out what schemes

40:29.680 --> 40:31.240
that the Zheng family is hatching.

40:31.240 --> 40:32.470
Why wouldn't they invite

40:32.470 --> 40:33.950
Tian Xing, who's also a gate commander?

40:33.950 --> 40:34.800
Liu Mu has a point.

40:34.800 --> 40:35.840
This must be a dangerous trip.

40:35.840 --> 40:37.840
We should protect Fan Yun together.

40:37.840 --> 40:39.510
You and Tian Xing will stand by outside.

40:39.510 --> 40:40.640
Let's play it by ear.

40:40.800 --> 40:41.630
No problem.

40:42.320 --> 40:42.990
Tian Xing,

40:43.280 --> 40:44.140
what about you?

40:45.030 --> 40:46.890
Rest assured. I'm up for the task.

40:53.240 --> 40:54.300
-Later...
-You...

40:57.470 --> 40:58.200
You go first.

40:58.680 --> 40:59.920
I just wanted to tell you

40:59.920 --> 41:02.320
that I heard
this Dragon's Beard Candy is tasty.

41:02.320 --> 41:03.430
Do you like to try some?

41:03.430 --> 41:04.200
Sure.

41:07.160 --> 41:08.160
What do you think?

41:11.840 --> 41:12.920
It really is tasty.

41:14.290 --> 41:15.490
I just meant to ask you

41:15.840 --> 41:17.200
if you've decided
what to do with the banquet

41:17.200 --> 41:18.260
in Jing City later.

41:20.680 --> 41:22.280
I'm still thinking about it.

41:24.760 --> 41:25.680
Hold there.

41:30.630 --> 41:31.680
Easy on the pastry.

41:31.680 --> 41:32.590
You've eaten much.

41:32.590 --> 41:34.850
Are you sure you have room for more later?

41:35.800 --> 41:36.990
Only when I am full

41:36.990 --> 41:39.070
can I have the energy
to deal with Zheng Jin.

41:39.070 --> 41:39.950
Besides,

41:39.950 --> 41:42.550
I wouldn't dare eat anything
prepared by them.

41:42.990 --> 41:43.590
Plus...

41:44.030 --> 41:44.680
Look.

41:45.550 --> 41:47.210
I've even brought my own wine.

41:48.950 --> 41:50.150
You are quite alert.

41:53.650 --> 41:55.550
I've also prepared something for you.

41:55.550 --> 41:56.240
What is it?

42:00.800 --> 42:01.550
What is this?

42:01.800 --> 42:04.390
A trinket from the Western Regions
that I brought from home.

42:04.390 --> 42:05.950
It was crafted by a master artisan.

42:05.950 --> 42:06.760
Look.

42:07.550 --> 42:09.200
When you shake one of the bells,

42:09.200 --> 42:11.000
the other one will sound as well.

42:12.470 --> 42:13.320
Really?

42:15.240 --> 42:17.400
This time, you have to be extra cautious

42:17.400 --> 42:18.780
when you cope with Zheng Jin.

42:18.780 --> 42:20.150
If there is any danger,

42:20.150 --> 42:21.320
just shake the bell.

42:21.680 --> 42:23.550
Then I'll come to you immediately.

42:23.550 --> 42:24.070
Got it?

42:25.360 --> 42:25.840
Got it.

42:30.130 --> 42:31.170
Eat up.

42:39.990 --> 42:41.610
This is enough acting.

42:41.840 --> 42:43.110
Don't push your luck

42:43.110 --> 42:44.990
or forget who you really are.

42:56.040 --> 42:57.440
So it's him.

42:58.450 --> 42:59.410
Gate Cdr. Fan,

42:59.470 --> 43:01.240
Eldest Young Master
is already waiting for you.

43:01.240 --> 43:02.240
This way, please.

43:31.220 --> 43:33.010
My Lady, are you saying

43:33.070 --> 43:34.240
that just now,

43:34.240 --> 43:36.510
someone whooshed past over there?

43:37.880 --> 43:38.760
But

43:38.760 --> 43:40.430
I didn't see anyone

43:40.430 --> 43:42.910
or hear a whoosh.

43:43.990 --> 43:44.990
You may leave now.

44:37.720 --> 44:38.720
Unlicensed salt?

44:43.360 --> 44:45.600
It's not a special kind of smuggled goods.
